Luigi runs a tacky pin-table joint in Soho which is frequented by questionable characters and kept under constant police surveillance. Luigi falls for Barbara, who is married to an abusive heavy gambler she loathes. Their burgeoning romance is interrupted when Luigi's ex-girlfriend, Angele, is found dead in his apartment.
